1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:03,723
Turn the method into one Minimum High-Signal Context Pack.

2
00:00:03,673 --> 00:00:11,326
It has six parts: Outcome, Operating Rules, Tool Map, Canonical Examples, Retrieval Index, and Working State.

3
00:00:11,326 --> 00:00:15,509
The pack is small enough to inspect and complete enough to guide real work.

4
00:00:15,509 --> 00:00:17,307
Part one is Outcome.

5
00:00:17,307 --> 00:00:23,903
State the goal, intended user, deliverable, acceptance criteria, and the decision the result must support.

6
00:00:23,903 --> 00:00:29,644
This prevents a fluent Agent from optimizing for an attractive output that does not solve the actual problem.

7
00:00:29,644 --> 00:00:31,913
Part two is Operating Rules.

8
00:00:31,913 --> 00:00:38,201
Record hard constraints, permissions, risk boundaries, escalation points, and stop conditions.

9
00:00:38,201 --> 00:00:44,096
Separate permanent rules from temporary assumptions so an old workaround does not silently become policy.

10
00:00:44,096 --> 00:00:47,951
Part three is the Tool Map, paired with Canonical Examples.

11
00:00:47,951 --> 00:00:56,057
For each tool, explain when to use it, what input it expects, what efficient output looks like, and which nearby tool it does not replace.

12
00:00:56,057 --> 00:01:00,576
Add two or three examples that show the main pattern and an important boundary.

13
00:01:00,576 --> 00:01:03,076
Part four is the Retrieval Index.

14
00:01:03,076 --> 00:01:08,490
Store lightweight handles to source material with a short purpose label and a trigger for opening it.

15
00:01:08,490 --> 00:01:13,278
The Agent should know both where the evidence lives and when the evidence becomes necessary.

16
00:01:13,278 --> 00:01:15,384
Part five is Working State.

17
00:01:15,384 --> 00:01:23,980
Record completed work, current focus, key decisions and evidence, unresolved questions, failed approaches, and the next concrete action.

18
00:01:23,980 --> 00:01:29,317
Update this state at milestones, then compact or archive the raw trace it replaces.

19
00:01:29,317 --> 00:01:33,403
First, anchor the AI Agent with Outcome and Operating Rules.

20
00:01:33,403 --> 00:01:38,990
Second, guide action with a Tool Map, Canonical Examples, and a Retrieval Index.

21
00:01:38,990 --> 00:01:43,971
Third, preserve continuity with a compact, regularly updated Working State.
